RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 1 6 1/2F Dirt CR: 37. Maiden Special Weight Purse 11000. FOR MAIDENS, FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 120 lbs.; Older, 123 lbs. Inf. y debutantes Allowed 4 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: MY SWEET GAL inside rally, driving. MISS UBINAS close up, regained second late. AMARGURA pressed pace, good effort. MI ABUELA BERTA A pressed pace outside, gave way. APRIL QUEEN weakened. SRTA. BLUE trailed.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 2 6 1/2F Dirt CR: 38. Claiming Purse 8100. FOR THREE YEAR OLDS. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since January 14 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since December 29 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since November 29 Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $20,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: COQUETON vied for lead, prevailed. YADIEL M. vied for lead, dropped back. GIAN KALEB bore out 1/4 pole, wide stretch. LUCAS VONFEDAK gamely place. ST ANDRES gamely place. ZENITSU weakened.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 3 1 1/16M Dirt CR: 60. Claiming Purse 6500. FOR NATIVE FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since January 14 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since December 29 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since November 29 Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $8,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: MAGO DE ORIENTE off pace, up in final strides. PENTAGRAMA led, drew clear, hung. ESTUPENDO close up, gave way. NEW MILIONAIRE improved position. PESCADOR DE SUENOS pressed pace, led, weakened. CONDOTTIERO E failed to menace. GALACTOR chased, weakened. BELLO SONERO set pace, weakened.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 4 6F Dirt CR: 77. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Weight, 121 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since January 14 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since December 29 Allowed 3 lbs. A Race Since November 29 Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 5 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 26. Maiden Claiming Purse 8600. FOR NATIVE MAIDENS, FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 118 lbs.; Older, 121 lbs. Clasif. $20,000 Allowed 1 lbs. Inferiores y debutantes Allowed 2 lbs. Claiming Price $20,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: SRTA. VEINTISIETE drew off. FAVISUS pressed pace, second best. YOHELYS vied for lead, gamely place. CARMENCITA improved position. VAPORIZADORA middle of pack, gave way. AMPARADA slow early, improved position. REINA MAYA improved position. TEMBLOROSA failed to menace. LA FRECUENCIA failed to menace. JARDIN FLORIDO dropped back. REAL ILUSION dropped back. SOMBRA GRIS bore out, did not finish.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 6 7F Dirt CR: 28. Maiden Claiming Purse 8600. FOR NATIVE MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 118 lbs.; Older, 121 lbs. Non-winners Of Races Allowed 1 lbs. Races Allowed 2 lbs. Claiming Price $20,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: ECLESIASTES much the best. EMPRENDEDOR drifted in a bit start, second best. CIRIBILLO off slowly, circled 6 wide. D' ARION between horses. RESISTENTE bit tight 600 between horses. JUGUETITO NUEVO bumped start, off slowly. COMPASIVO close up, weakened. DON NICA failed to menace. NUBE NEGRA pressed pace, dropped back. CAPITAN PIZARRO dropped back. SAAQ THE TROOPER off slowly, no menace. POCHOLO off slowly, no menace.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 7 6F Dirt CR: 46. Maiden Claiming Purse 6000. FOR MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 120 lbs.; Older, 123 lbs. Clasif. $4,000 y debutantes Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: BARRIO SAN JOSE set pace, just lasted. FUTURISTIC too late, short. SNEAKY DREAM off slowly, up for third. MR. PIONEERING no rally. OVERSTATED improved position.
